 Digital to Market High-Powered Workstations: The Maynard, Mass.-based computer 
maker said the workstations are intended for scientists, engineers and business 
people who need lots of power to run complex software and handle huge 
databases.It is the first major product launch for Digital Equipment Corp. 
after several weeks of announcements of cost-cutting actions aimed at restoring 
