<HEADLINE>
<P>
SET TO SELF-DESTRUCT? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * There appear to be as many special interest groups and cult followers in our 
country as there are politicians.Now, that is scary! I give our ever-failing 
system of government 10 years (plus or minus five years) before 
self-destructing. There is too much political greed and corruption going 
