<HEADLINE>
<P>
MINI-TOUR SEEKS ENTRIES FOR CAMARILLO GOLF EVENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Fairway Assn. is seeking entries for its inaugural professional tournament 
Monday at Camarillo Springs Golf Course in Camarillo. 
</P>
<P>
 The Fairway Assn., a mini-tour that hopes to rival the Golden State Tour, is 
based in Newbury Park. The tournament is open to professional and low-handicap 
players. A purse of $3,400 will be offered if the field grows to 40 or more 
players. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: 805-498-6580. 
</P>
</TEXT>
